<td align="left"><span id="req:rgsmart.oplat.10">RGSMART.OPLAT.10<a class="headerlink" href="12-index-rgsmart.html#req:rgsmart.oplat.10" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
