</tr>
<tr class="odd">
<td align="left"><span id="req:rgsmart.oplat.11">RGSMART.OPLAT.11<a class="headerlink" href="12-index-rgsmart.html#req:rgsmart.oplat.11" title="Permalink to this span"> <img src='permalink.png' title='' width="0.8em"/></a></span></td>
<td align="left">The open platform SHOULD support to limit the resources used by open
platform environments and applications including CPU time, number of
threads, RAM, and Sockets used.</td>
</tr>
</table>

